subject: OpenPOWER: Updates for removing duplicate code
commitMessage:
OpenPOWER: Updates for removing duplicate code

Classes dump_manager_hostboot and dump_manager_hardware
doing identical operations except the entry type is
different, so combined there two as a template class
to remove duplicate code. The new template class will be
handling all host dumps stored on the BMC.

Signed-off-by: Dhruvaraj Subhashchandran <dhruvaraj@in.ibm.com>
Change-Id: I85e7bc15eb240be84ce3eafa559e176e399e70d5
